<grid_rows>  		- number of rows in the grid (positive integer)
<grid_cols>  		- number of columns in the grid (positive integer)
<sim_time>   		- number of iterations
<temp_file>  		- name of the file containing the initial temperature values of each cell
<power_file> 		- name of the file containing the dissipated power values of each cell
<out_file> 		    - name of the output file

example:
tornado  -m tornado.examples/uk.ac.manchester.tornado.examples.rodinia.hotspot.Hotspot 64 64 4 tornado-examples/src/main/java/uk/ac/manchester/tornado/examples/rodinia/data/hotspot/temp_64 tornado-examples/src/main/java/uk/ac/manchester/tornado/examples/rodinia/data/hotspot/power_64 tornado-examples/src/main/java/uk/ac/manchester/tornado/examples/rodinia/hotspot/out_64